Package: FerroScore
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Ferroptosis Score from Transcriptomic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jiaqi Teng
Maintainer: Jiaqi Teng <tengjq3@mail2.sysu.edu.cn>
Description: FerroScore is a package that quantifies ferroptosis activity based on transcriptomic data (RNA-seq or scRNA-seq). It enables quantitative assessment in individual samples or single cells by systematically integrating key molecular features and network topology related to ferroptosis.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    edgeR,
    stringr,
    igraph,
    ggraph,
    STRINGdb,
    dplyr,
    clusterProfiler,
    org.Mm.eg.db,
    org.Hs.eg.db,
    enrichplot,
    ggplot2,
    GOplot,
    openxlsx
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
